==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undecennial
<hw>Un`de*cen"ni*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Undecennary</er>, and cf. <er>Decennial</er>.]</ety> <def>Occurring
or observed every eleventh year; belonging to, or continuing, a period
of eleven years; undecennary; <as>as, an <ex>undecennial</ex>
festival</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

